        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Menands%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Albany Rural Cemetery, founded in 1841, is one of the earliest American rural cemeteries, modeled after Paris’s Père Lachaise and featuring winding paths and monumental monuments.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4,
        14
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
